    "Limitations of AI techniques in developing personalized medicines are also highlighted, along with areas for further research.",
    "III.Healthcare Chatbots and Virtual Assistants: AI-powered chatbots are revolutionizing the healthcare industry by providing virtual assistants that can manage conversations through speech or textual methods [27].",
